quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  6,125,"Kho ulia owa Nyasaye yenya okhumulunjisia, yanguyinjia eshilifu shishie shibe nobwihotselefu (obusalamu). Ne ulia wa Nyasaye yenya okhukosia, akholanga eshilifu shiaye okhuba eshitiyifu, eshisiro shinga uninanga mwikulu khubutinyu. Endio nilwa Nyasaye aretsanga obufundu khubalia abalasuubilanga tawe."
  6,126,"Ne ino ni injila ya Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, ingololofu. Toto khwamala okhwinoosilia tsinyaali tsiefu abandu betsulilanga."
  6,127,"Balinyoola tsinzu tsiomulembe okhurula khu Nyasaye wabu Omulesi. Naye niye omulindi wabu, khulwa kalia akabakholanga."
  6,128,"Ne inyanga ya alibakhung’asia boosi, “Enywe omukanda kwa majini, toto enywe mwabukula abalondi abanji okhurula mubandu.” Mana abetsa babu mubandu baliboola mbu, “Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, khwakhonyananga efwe ninabo mana khulile khubise biefu biawakhurererao.” Nyasaye aliboola mbu; “Mumulilo nimwo eshimenyo shienyu, mwitsa okhwikhalamwo tsinyanga tsioosi, halali shia Nyasaye achama. Toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye Owamachesi po, Omumanyi muno."
  6,129,"Ne endio nilwa khukholanga abandu ababii okhuyanzana abeene khubeene okhubeela kalia akabakholanga."
  6,130,"“Enywe omukanda kwa amajini, nende abandu, koo, shibabeetselakhwo Abarumwa okhurula mwinywe, babenoosilinjia tsinyaali tsianje, ne nibabekanyisilia omukhung’ano okwa inyanga yenyu ya lelo?” Baliboola mbu; “Khuli abaloli khwifwe abeene.” Ne obulamu bwokhushialo bwabakatia. Ne nibelolela abeene mbu toto bali abakhayi."
  6,131,"Endio nilwa okhuba mbu, Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi shiyali wokhusishia tsingongo khububii, abamenyi batsio nibakorerwe tawe."